data.description: ALL AGES WELCOME!  Gated community, Lake View Townhouse with 2 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, 1 Car Garage. The 1st floor features Tile Floor & 2nd Floor with Carpeting. The Kitchen with Stainless-Steel Appliances, Eat in Kitchen with Pass Thru window.  Relax in your private Screened Patio and enjoy the Lake View. Interior Natural light through the Home! The Community features Clubhouse, amenities include Pool, Playground Area, Tennis, Volleyball Courts & Fitness Center. Turtle Cay is Close to many Attractions nearby, Ball Park of the Palm Beach's & Rapids Water Park. Minutes' Drive to Palm Beach Gardens Mall & Palm Beach Outlets, Restaurants, Beaches, PBI Airport, easy access to I-95 and Turnpike.
